| user_id | surname | firstname | email            | 

+---------+---------+-----------+------------------+ 

| 1001    | Smith   | John      | john@email.com   | 

| 1002    | Brown   | Emma      | emma@email.com   | 

+---------+---------+-----------+------------------+ 

