Query 7: List all orders with product details 

SQL: 

SELECT o.order_id, u.firstname, u.surname, p.product_name, oi.quantity, oi.price 

FROM `ORDER` o 

INNER JOIN USER u ON o.user_id = u.user_id 

INNER JOIN ORDER_ITEM oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id 

INNER JOIN PRODUCT p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id 

ORDER BY o.order_id; 

