Query 14: List all reviews for a specific product (product_id = 1) 

SQL:

SELECT r.review_id, u.surname, u.firstname, r.rating, r.comment, r.review_date 

FROM REVIEW r 

INNER JOIN USER u ON r.user_id = u.user_id 

WHERE r.product_id = 1 

ORDER BY r.review_date DESC; 

