Query 15: Find the average rating for each product 

SQL:

SELECT p.product_id, p.product_name, AVG(r.rating) AS avg_rating, COUNT(r.review_id) AS total_reviews 

FROM PRODUCT p 

LEFT JOIN REVIEW r ON p.product_id = r.product_id 

GROUP BY p.product_id, p.product_name 

ORDER BY avg_rating DESC; 

Sample Output: 
